name: Contacts History
tagline: Find people in your address book based on where and when you meet them.
body:
# Contacts History Find people in your address book based on where and when you meet them.
You can filter your contacts: - recent added contacts - contacts added today, this week, month - contacts added in a specific date - contacts added between two dates - contacts added in a specific city or country
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
